# SEO Implementation Walkthrough

## What Was Accomplished

### 1. Core SEO Infrastructure

| File | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| [src/app/hooks/useSEO.ts](file:///d:/Pranavayu%20Website/src/app/hooks/useSEO.ts) | Custom hook — imperatively sets `<title>`, `<meta>`, canonical, OG, Twitter & injects JSON-LD `<script>` blocks per route |
| [src/app/seo/schemas.ts](file:///d:/Pranavayu%20Website/src/app/seo/schemas.ts) | Centralized JSON-LD schema factory — exports named schemas + builder functions |

