## Next Steps (Recommended)

1. **Verify with a real domain** — Update all `pranavayu.com` references in [schemas.ts](file:///d:/Pranavayu%20Website/src/app/seo/schemas.ts) and [index.html](file:///d:/Pranavayu%20Website/index.html) with the actual deployed domain
2. **Submit sitemap to Google Search Console** — [search.google.com/search-console](https://search.google.com/search-console)
3. **Create `public/images/og-default.webp`** — An 1200×630px branded image for social sharing (referenced in OG tags)
4. **Consider pre-rendering** — For a Vite SPA, tools like `vite-plugin-prerender` or deploying on a host with SSR support (Vercel) will enable full crawler indexing
